  "texts": [
    "We query the 𝑘-th LLM 𝑓 (𝑘) with the samples in X and retrieves corresponding scores 𝑦 (𝑘) = {𝑓 (𝑘) (𝑥 1), 𝑓 (𝑘) (𝑥 2),..., 𝑓 (𝑘) (𝑥 𝑁)}.",
